==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Malebranchism
<hw>Male*branch"ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The
philosophical system of <persfn><etsep>Malebranche</etsep></persfn>, an
eminent French metaphysician. The fundamental doctrine of his system is
that the mind can not have knowledge of anything external to itself
except in its relation to God.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>male chauvinism</ent>⟦br⟧
